text: Rhabdochitina is an extinct genus of chitinozoans. It was described by Alfred Eisenack in 1931.Rhabdochitina at ChitDB: Chitinozoans of Baltica. ==Species== * Rhabdochitina gracilis Eisenack, 1962 * Rhabdochitina magna Eisenack, 1931 * Rhabdochitina sera Nestor, 2007 ==References== Category:Prehistoric marine animals Category:Fossil taxa described in 1931
title: Rhabdochitina
